SetPatch >NIL:
;AddBuffers >NIL: WORK: 15
;FailAt 21
Resident >NIL: C:Assign PURE
Resident >NIL: C:Execute PURE
Echo " "
Ask "Mount RAD (Y/N)?: "
IF WARN
Assign >NIL: RAD: EXISTS
IF WARN
Echo " "
Echo "Setting Up RAD: - Please Wait."
Echo " "
Mount RAD:
IF NOT EXISTS RAD:S
MakeDir RAD:S
ENDIF
IF NOT EXISTS RAD:C
MakeDir RAD:C
ENDIF
IF NOT EXISTS RAD:Devs
MakeDir RAD:Devs
ENDIF
IF NOT EXISTS RAD:Devs/KeyMaps
MakeDir RAD:Devs/KeyMaps
ENDIF
Copy >NIL: :C/SetPatch RAD:C quiet noreq
Copy >NIL: :C/SetMap RAD:C quiet noreq
Copy >NIL: :C/MakeDir RAD:C quiet noreq
Copy >NIL: :C/LoadWb RAD:C quiet noreq
Copy >NIL: :Prefs/startup-sequence RAD:S quiet noreq
Copy >NIL: :Devs/system-configuration RAD:Devs quiet noreq
Copy >NIL: :Devs/KeyMaps/gb RAD:Devs/KeyMaps quiet noreq
Relabel DRIVE RAD: Bootable_RAM
Wait 5
DiskChange DEVICE RAD:
Echo "RAD Mounted and Bootable."
Else
Echo "RAD Already Exists."
ENDIF
ENDIF
Echo " "
MakeDir Ram:Env Ram:Env/Sys Ram:Clipboards Ram:T
Ask "Copy ENVARC To Ram Disk (Y/N)?: "
IF WARN
Copy >NIL: ENVARC: Ram:Env all quiet noreq
Echo " "
Echo "ENVARC Has Been Copied Into RAM."
ENDIF
Assign ENV: Ram:Env
Assign CLIPS: Ram:ClipBoards
Assign T: Ram:T
Assign REXX: Ram:T
Assign PRINTERS: Devs:Printers
Assign KEYMAPS: Devs:Keymaps
Assign LOCALE: WORK:Locale
Assign LIBS: WORK:Classes ADD
Assign HELP: Locale:Help DEFER
Assign Emodules: WORK:Emodules
Echo " "
IF EXISTS s:user-startup
Echo "Executing User-Startup Sequence - Please Wait."
Execute s:user-startup
Echo " "
Echo "User-Startup Has Been Executed."
Echo " "
ENDIF
Ask "Run IPrefs (Y/N)?: "
IF WARN
Echo " "
Echo "Note: You might have to click on an - IPrefs Requesters - to fully"
Echo "      enable IPrefs/ENViroment. It depends on the system, etc."
IPrefs
ENDIF
ConClip
SetMap gb
Resident Execute REMOVE
Resident Assign REMOVE
LoadWB
EndCli >NIL:
